## Quick Start

```bash
# Create feature branch
git checkout -b feature/my-feature develop

# After making changes
git add <files>
git commit -m "feat(scope): concise description"
git push origin feature/my-feature

# Create PR (if GitHub CLI is installed)
gh pr create --draft
```
